<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 02:28:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列安全部门消息来源：蒙面定居者在约旦河西岸哈瓦拉村焚烧巴勒斯坦车辆</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-live/security-source-masked-settlers-torch-palestinian-vehicles-in-w-bank-village-of-hawara/00000190-e281-d9bf-a195-e789725e0000</link><description>白宫：拜登-内塔尼亚胡将于周四会面；特朗普定于周五在海湖庄园举行会议 ■ 获救人质告诉内塔尼亚胡：加沙最困难的部分是听到你说战争将是长期的 ■ 世界卫生组织称，脊髓灰质炎病毒在加沙传播的“风险很高” ■ 巴勒斯坦各派签署结束宣言官方媒体报道称，中国会谈后存在分歧 ■ 巴勒斯坦报道：哈马斯、约旦河西岸图尔卡尔姆的阿克萨烈士旅首领在以色列国防军无人机袭击中丧生 ■ 内塔尼亚胡在华盛顿对人质家属表示：“他们返回的条件正在成熟”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 02:20:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-live/security-source-masked-settlers-torch-palestinian-vehicles-in-w-bank-village-of-hawara/00000190-e281-d9bf-a195-e789725e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将于周四在白宫会见拜登，周五将在海湖庄园会见特朗普</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-meet-biden-at-white-house-on-thursday-trump-at-mar-a-lago-on-friday/00000190-e140-d9bf-a195-e5c841d80000</link><description>白宫确认，拜登总统将在以色列总理向国会发表讲话以及拜登向全国发表黄金时段讲话后不到 24 小时会见内塔尼亚胡，他将在讲话中首次阐述他不竞选连任的决定</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 20:53:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-meet-biden-at-white-house-on-thursday-trump-at-mar-a-lago-on-friday/00000190-e140-d9bf-a195-e5c841d80000</guid></item><item><title>议会为人力资源机构雇员提供免遭性骚扰的保护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/knesset-gives-protections-against-sexual-harassment-to-manpower-agency-employees/00000190-e11b-dab4-afb9-f37b83420000</link><description>该修正案还将禁止歧视性骚扰投诉者的规定扩大到通过此类机构雇用的工人</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 20:08:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/knesset-gives-protections-against-sexual-harassment-to-manpower-agency-employees/00000190-e11b-dab4-afb9-f37b83420000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列总检察长拒绝上诉，2021 年骚乱中阿拉伯人被犹太人杀害的案件仍将结案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/case-of-arab-killed-by-jews-in-2021-riots-to-remain-closed-as-israels-ag-rejects-appeal/00000190-e107-d041-a3f4-e9eff21a0000</link><description>穆萨·哈苏纳的家人声称，此案的调查存在缺陷，是迫于政治压力而结束的。总检察长驳回上诉的决定并未解决这些主张</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 19:42:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/case-of-arab-killed-by-jews-in-2021-riots-to-remain-closed-as-israels-ag-rejects-appeal/00000190-e107-d041-a3f4-e9eff21a0000</guid></item><item><title>美国犹太人在哈里斯-夏皮罗选票中看到希望，同时准备迎接反犹太主义风暴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-23/ty-article/.highlight/american-jews-see-hope-in-harris-shapiro-ticket-while-bracing-for-an-antisemitic-storm/00000190-e04f-d2bf-a7f9-f0ff63e40000</link><description>在庆祝卡玛拉·哈里斯成为民主党推定提名人的同时，美国犹太人应该做好准备，迎接唐纳德·特朗普的基地将面临的坎坷之路。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 19:34:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-23/ty-article/.highlight/american-jews-see-hope-in-harris-shapiro-ticket-while-bracing-for-an-antisemitic-storm/00000190-e04f-d2bf-a7f9-f0ff63e40000</guid></item><item><title>教育部长表示，以色列与黎巴嫩边境附近的学校不会在秋季重新开放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/schools-near-israels-border-with-lebanon-wont-reopen-in-fall-education-minister-says/00000190-e0d0-d566-adfa-ebf213690000</link><description>教育部长约夫·基什在解释他九月份不重新开放北部社区学校的决定时告诉北部市长，“我们别无选择，只能决定对黎巴嫩发动一场激烈的战争”。自战争爆发以来，超过 16,000 名学生从北方撤离</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 19:10:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/schools-near-israels-border-with-lebanon-wont-reopen-in-fall-education-minister-says/00000190-e0d0-d566-adfa-ebf213690000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 291 天：内塔尼亚胡表示人质返回的条件“正在成熟”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-291-netanyahu-says-conditions-for-hostages-return-are-ripening/00000190-e04f-d548-a3ba-eecf4cd70001</link><description>世界卫生组织警告，由于健康和卫生条件不佳，加沙及其他地区小儿麻痹症爆发的风险很高。定居者 ■ 哈马斯和法塔赫称他们签署了宣言，誓言组建联合政府 ■ 战争开始 291 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 17:10:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-291-netanyahu-says-conditions-for-hostages-return-are-ripening/00000190-e04f-d548-a3ba-eecf4cd70001</guid></item><item><title>Einav Zangauker 发布了她的儿子 Matan 在加沙被囚禁的镜头以及他 10 月 7 日的短信</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/einav-zangauker-releases-footage-of-her-son-in-gaza-captivity-with-his-final-messages/00000190-e075-d9bf-a195-e5fdab440000</link><description>在视频中，马坦骑在汗尤尼斯的一辆摩托车上，背景中有人欢呼，这可能是在他被绑架后不久拍摄的。他给家人的最后信息显示没有警察在场，并恳求道：“军队什么时候来？”他们已经占领了一半的基布兹”</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 16:56:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/einav-zangauker-releases-footage-of-her-son-in-gaza-captivity-with-his-final-messages/00000190-e075-d9bf-a195-e5fdab440000</guid></item><item><title>世卫组织警告加沙及其边境地区的脊髓灰质炎风险很高，因为水卫生条件恶劣</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/who-warns-of-high-polio-risk-in-gaza-and-beyond-its-borders-amid-dire-water-sanitation/00000190-dfde-dab4-afb9-fffeebf10000</link><description>尽管在沿海飞地的污水样本中发现了这种病毒，但以色列军方表示，没有任何加沙居民感染这种疾病的信息；本周，以色列国防军开始为以色列士兵开展脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种活动</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:53:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/who-warns-of-high-polio-risk-in-gaza-and-beyond-its-borders-amid-dire-water-sanitation/00000190-dfde-dab4-afb9-fffeebf10000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其谴责以色列调频发布了埃尔多安婴儿时期躺在伊朗最高领袖腿上的人工智能图像</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/turkey-blasts-israeli-fm-for-ai-image-of-erdogan-as-baby-on-lap-of-iran-supreme-leader/00000190-dfb8-dbe5-a7fa-fffa967e0000</link><description>外交部之间的相互争执标志着土以关系持续恶化的又一步，这种关系十多年前就开始紧张，自加沙战争爆发以来迅速恶化</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:27:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/turkey-blasts-israeli-fm-for-ai-image-of-erdogan-as-baby-on-lap-of-iran-supreme-leader/00000190-dfb8-dbe5-a7fa-fffa967e0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯、法塔赫在华签署巴勒斯坦“团结”协议，无实际意义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/hamas-fatah-sign-palestinian-unity-agreement-in-china-with-no-practical-significance/00000190-df7d-d851-afbe-df7d78fa0000</link><description>消息人士称，巴勒斯坦各派就合作达成了总体谅解，并接受巴解组织作为组建巴勒斯坦民族政府的行政框架，但法塔赫高级官员表示，联合声明主要是为了表达对东道主中国的尊重</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 14:18:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/hamas-fatah-sign-palestinian-unity-agreement-in-china-with-no-practical-significance/00000190-df7d-d851-afbe-df7d78fa0000</guid></item><item><title>向国会发表讲话是内塔尼亚胡个人的胜利，也是以色列的又一次失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/why-netanyahus-congress-speech-will-be-an-even-bigger-failure-than-all-his-previous-ones/00000190-df64-d566-adfa-ff6661730000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡向国会发表空洞、失败、疏远的演讲的悠久历史</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 13:46:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/why-netanyahus-congress-speech-will-be-an-even-bigger-failure-than-all-his-previous-ones/00000190-df64-d566-adfa-ff6661730000</guid></item><item><title>拜登已将以色列制裁精灵从瓶子里放出来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/biden-has-let-the-israel-sanctions-genie-out-of-the-bottle/00000190-dfb1-dbe5-a7fa-fffbfbc50000</link><description>随着加沙战争的继续，越来越多的国家正在实施这些措施，而且该清单的规模可能会扩大到可能损害以色列经济的程度</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 13:37:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/biden-has-let-the-israel-sanctions-genie-out-of-the-bottle/00000190-dfb1-dbe5-a7fa-fffbfbc50000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡废除以色列新闻自由的总体计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/inside-netanyahus-masterplan-to-dismantle-the-freedom-of-the-press-in-israel/00000190-df02-d041-a3f4-ffee92ca0000</link><description>热门电视政治脱口秀节目的取消暴露了内塔尼亚胡在以色列报道的关键时刻如何努力摧毁独立新闻业、恐吓记者并压制对其行为和政策的任何批评，以及美英寡头如何帮助他</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 11:46:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/inside-netanyahus-masterplan-to-dismantle-the-freedom-of-the-press-in-israel/00000190-df02-d041-a3f4-ffee92ca0000</guid></item><item><title>谁是卡塔尔文件事件的幕后黑手，以 20 万欧元出售针对内塔尼亚胡的“证据”？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-people-behind-the-qatar-documents-affair-selling-evidence-against-netanyahu/00000190-dabc-d9bf-a195-ffbc14fb0000</link><description>据称证明卡塔尔向内塔尼亚胡提供资金的耸人听闻的出版物背后隐藏着一个以每页数万美元出售可疑文件的网络</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 11:45:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-people-behind-the-qatar-documents-affair-selling-evidence-against-netanyahu/00000190-dabc-d9bf-a195-ffbc14fb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队证实，两名巴勒斯坦激进分子指挥官在西岸图尔卡姆袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-confirms-two-hamas-commanders-killed-in-tul-karm-strike-in-west-bank/00000190-dedc-d041-a3f4-fffeee020000</link><description>以色列军方表示，自战争爆发以来，他们在该市发动了约 50 次空袭，最近的行动目的是应对爆炸装置的威胁</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 11:34:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-confirms-two-hamas-commanders-killed-in-tul-karm-strike-in-west-bank/00000190-dedc-d041-a3f4-fffeee020000</guid></item><item><title>圣经前以色列使用昆虫制成的早期红色染料</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-07-23/ty-article/early-red-dye-made-from-insects-used-in-pre-biblical-israel/00000190-dea5-d851-afbe-dfa5cf560000</link><description>死海头骨洞中发现的数百件织物碎片可以追溯到红铜并用时代到罗马时期，其中一些是惊人的猩红色</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 10:37:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-07-23/ty-article/early-red-dye-made-from-insects-used-in-pre-biblical-israel/00000190-dea5-d851-afbe-dfa5cf560000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的公务飞机首飞飞往华盛顿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-official-plane-makes-maiden-flight-to-washington/00000190-de9c-d041-a3f4-fffef0a60000</link><description>锡安之翼于 2016 年购买，为以色列国家元首服务，现已成为奢华的象征、与公众脱节和浪费公共资金</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 10:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-official-plane-makes-maiden-flight-to-washington/00000190-de9c-d041-a3f4-fffef0a60000</guid></item><item><title>日本对参与暴力侵害巴勒斯坦人的四名以色列定居者实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/asia-and-australia/2024-07-23/ty-article/japan-slaps-sanctions-on-israeli-settlers-involved-in-violence-against-palestinians/00000190-de63-dab4-afb9-ff6b48ab0000</link><description>以色列内阁首席秘书表示，该国强烈敦促以色列政府“与国际社会合作，彻底冻结定居点活动”</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 09:37:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/asia-and-australia/2024-07-23/ty-article/japan-slaps-sanctions-on-israeli-settlers-involved-in-violence-against-palestinians/00000190-de63-dab4-afb9-ff6b48ab0000</guid></item><item><title>备忘录称，以色列网络安全公司 Wiz 取消了与谷歌 230 亿美元的交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/israeli-cybersecurity-company-wiz-calls-off-23-bln-deal-with-google-memo-says/00000190-ddb6-d548-a3ba-fffe22710000</link><description>早些时候有报道称，谷歌母公司 Alphabet 正在就收购该公司进行深入谈判。 Wiz 首席执行官：“虽然我们对收到的报价感到受宠若惊，但我们选择继续打造 Wiz”</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 06:03:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/israeli-cybersecurity-company-wiz-calls-off-23-bln-deal-with-google-memo-says/00000190-ddb6-d548-a3ba-fffe22710000</guid></item></channel></rss>